In `style.css`, implement:

**Global resets and base:**
```css
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  background: #0a0a0f;
  color: #ffffff;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}
```

**Pad grid layout:**
```css
#pad-chassis {
  background: #000000;
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 2rem;
  box-shadow: 0 0 2rem rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
}

#pad-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
  width: min(85vmin, 600px);
  aspect-ratio: 1;
}

.pad {
  background: #1a1a1f;
  border: 3px solid var(--pad-color, #333);
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vmin, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: #ffffff;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  /* Dim resting glow */
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 0.5rem var(--pad-color),
    inset 0 0 2rem rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}

.pad:focus {
  outline: 2px solid var(--pad-color);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

**Responsive scaling:**
```css
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  body { padding: 1rem; }
  #pad-chassis { padding: 1rem; }
  #pad-grid { gap: 0.5rem; }
}
```

